==Swedish==
===Suffix===
'''-a'''

#After an adjective (''absolute''), indicates that the corresponding noun is either in plural, ''or'' that it is definite form, of ''non-masculine'' gender
#Used to create new [[verb]]s from a noun, in the [[infinitive]].

====Examples====
*[[disk#Swedish|disk]] (dishes)
*:''att disk'''a''''' - to do the dishes
*[[Lås]] (lock)
*:''att lås'''a''' en dörr'' - to lock a door

[[Category:Swedish suffixes]]
